com.serena.dmclient.objects
Interface ItemTypeCMRules

All Superinterfaces:
DimensionsObject
public interface ItemTypeCMRules
extends DimensionsObject

Represents change management rules that can be enabled for an item type. Change management rules control the development of items of the specified item type.
